{"tid":770752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美競賽】大鑊！德勤：美國5G發展落後於中國","createTime":"2018-08-07T10:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T11:50:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"36638d7adc186902606b7a157b4949cce80d46ab","tid":770752,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"德勤發表報告稱，美國在建造5G通訊的花費被中國超過，並有可能失去潛在的經濟利益。<br />\n<br />\n報告發現，中國目前支持5G通訊的基站是美國的10多倍，單單2017年首三個月，中國手機基站公司和運營商增加的基站，比美國之前三年所設的還多。中國自2015年以來花費已比美國多出240億美元，並已建設35萬個新的無線基站，而美國建設的則不到3萬個。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報告又指，由於5G帶來「未開發經濟潛力的時代」，故率先採用5G通訊的國家將獲得「不成正比的收益」。德勤在一項聲明中表示，美國想保有競爭力和最終取得領導地位的話，就應謹慎評估5G之爭及迅速採取行動，認為美國或有可能迎頭趕上，但建議美國調整政策以減少建置5G時間、鼓勵運營商合作、成立一個統計及最佳作法的資料庫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180807/58533447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58533447&d=CByY6opXVAj6kKRM0DXF1TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=35aee39d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58533447&h=ac74fe09\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180807/58533447</a>"},{"pid":"efe50903e58e8731d773a523662037aa94015c3e","tid":770752,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"制裁屎為咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a3e1f4111dc80988e4d39d78c53d76f7731bdf","tid":770752,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"咁可以出兵消滅美國未？"},{"pid":"60d7e0f7f34ad449afd7f54f11e361e273259401","tid":770752,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:20:44.000Z","msg":"5g上google?"},{"pid":"0d8df0c0c688b2b6af2025d772e1ae9fd0393da7","tid":770752,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep